snippet.title: Dead Cells: The End is Near
snippet.description:
Hey there Dead Cells fans! The time has come… Update 35 is now out on Steam and Consoles! 

Take command of the beheaded once more, and venture into cursed biomes with an array of new weapons and legendary affixes at your disposal! Tackle new enemy types while juggling the looming threat of the curse… Don’t worry though, you’ll die in style with over 40 new head customization options at your fingertips. 

From everyone at Evil Empire and Motion Twin, thank you for playing Dead Cells. We look forward to seeing your endless struggle continue for years to come.

Check out Evil Empire's next game
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2717880/The_Rogue_Prince_of_Persia/

Check out Motion Twin's next game
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1911610/Windblown/
